The paper deals with content delivery over a broadcast channel with erasures, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT). It also involves the use of caching, which is a topic in computer networks (cs.NI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes a joint caching and channel coding scheme, which is a topic in signal processing (cs.SI) and communication theory (cs.COM).
